"                                    formality;&amp;nbsp;it’s a powerful act "
"of solidarity. It’s\n"
"                                    choosing to stand with those who have "
"been silenced, to defend\n"
"                                    the rights that protect us all, and to "
"fight for a future where\n"
"                                    no one is left behind."
